snippet.title: Where is Pushpa? | Pushpa 2 - The Rule üî• | Hindi | Allu Arjun | Sukumar | Rashmika | Fahadh Faasil
snippet.description:
#WhereIsPushpa #Pushpa2TheRule #AlluArjun

Where is Pushpa? Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Hindi Glimpse !!!

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings,  the film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Suneel, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad, with cinematography and editing were performed by Miroslaw Kuba Brozek and Karthika Srinivas respectively.

#hernekatha #Laurokokatha

Krishna Lawad from Dehimandu, Baitadi has an interesting but a tough profession. He goes deep into the forest to find sticks. With his inherited craftsmanship, he turns them into strong and beautiful walking sticks and sells them in the market. 





‚ù§Ô∏è A warm and gentle request ‚ù§Ô∏è
Herne Katha is amazingly proudly independent journalism. We are free from political or corporate influence. If you love our work and believe in our absolute, astonishing and proud independent journalism please consider supporting us (please only support us if you are financially comfortable). Herne Katha will be free forever, no matter what.

==== Why Herne Katha? ====
People behind Herne Katha spent 15 years of their lives doing journalism. One day they realised the need to tell more beautiful and inspiring stories of people, the real people. 

üëÄüëÄüëÄ Herne Katha üëÄüëÄüëÄ
Herne Katha is a web series produced by Tana Bana Digital in Nepal. We tell stories of people in the format of short documentaries. New episode of Herne Katha is published on  every  alternate Tuesdays (15 days) on YouTube. You can also watch Herne  Katha on Kantipur  Television every Tuesday 6:30 PM.

üíåüíåüíå Share your Story üíåüíåüíå 
If you have a story that is suitable for Herne Katha, please do not hesitate to contact us. 

üí≤üí≤üí≤ For Advertisers üí≤üí≤üí≤

üé∂üé∂üé∂ For Singers and Musicians üé∂üé∂üé∂ 
If you are an emerging artist or musicians, we need you. We want to feature your creation in our episodes and support you to get noticed by thousands of our audience. 


üé®üé®üé® For all Creatives üé®üé®üé®
Have an idea about anything? Anything related to telling people's stories in bold and beautiful style. Share your ideas with us. We love ideas.

snippet.description:
Boyfriend is a song where Dino James portrays the insecurities and toxicity that an individual can go through in a relationship and the trauma that follows if they let themselves fall deep into the dark hole of insecurities. An uncomfortable truth that a lot of people face. Through this song, Dino James has a strong message, ‚ÄúIf this is what people face, best for both parties to walk away. snippet.title: A Soldier's Reaction. #holiday  #shorts
snippet.description:
A military officer attempts to hunt down a terrorist, destroy a terrorist gang and deactivate the sleeper cells under his command.
Cast - Akshay Kumar, Sonakshi Sinha, Freddy Daruwala 
Directed by - A.R. Murugadoss


"Holiday: A Soldier Is Never Off Duty" is a high-octane action film which showcases Akshay Kumar's skills as an action star. The movie boasts of thrilling and intense action sequences, a well-written screenplay, and good performances from the lead actors. The plot of the movie revolves around the life of a soldier on vacation who stumbles upon a terrorist plot and decides to put a stop to it. He has to work with a local police officer and other officials to track down the terrorists and prevent them from carrying out their plan. The film also deals with themes of patriotism and selfless service to the nation. Overall, "Holiday: A Soldier Is Never Off Duty" is a well-crafted action thriller that is sure to keep audiences on the edge of their seats.
